Builder Dash Game






Norbord presents Builder Dash for iPad & iPhone
You can now play with the same great Norbord products you build with. Jump into the side-scrolling adventure that takes you through the worksite in order to deliver your OSB! But beware of the bad weather which threatens to slow you down at every turn – so better make sure to choose the right OSB for the job! Download it for FREE today.





