Careers at Norbord

Excellent people make excellent business.
Our success comes from hiring skilled and talented team members in all areas of our business. At Norbord, we are dedicated to developing and retaining a strong and committed workforce that ensures we remain at the front of manufacturing excellence. We are committed to teamwork and safety without compromise. Click here to browse our current opportunities.









