            Norbord Alabama is a branch location of Norbord, an international wood based panel board producer. The company s premiere product is oriented strand board, an engineered wood panel product designed for home construction and industrial use known for its strength, stiffness and consistency. Norbord s additional products include: TallWall, which are panels used for wall sheathing; web stock, which is used in the manufacture of wooden I-Joists; solar board, which is a decking product used for roofs and exterior walls; Stabledge, an advanced form of oriented strand board; and Windstorm, which is a sturdy paneling used for protection against weather related damage. Norbord Alabama maintains facilities in Lanatt, Ala.
          






















